						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription which belongs to the period of the Vijayanagar and it records the gift of villages to the temples. It also mentions that this grant was engraved an stone by Basava-Bhaṭṭa, Pādhyāra and the chief accountant <hi rend="italic">(Sēnabāva)-Gaṇakāgarēśara</hi>, Timmap[p]a. </p>						

