<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śubhamastu^1^ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> lēpākṣi vīrabhadrasya <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pāpanāśēśvarasya ca <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīrāmasya ca saṁbaṁdhi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> grāmasīmā
<lb n="2"/>śāsanaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīrēśa nijabhakta śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīrapaṁṇaniyōgataḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīcāṭakūra basavābhaṭō pādhyāya ya
<lb n="3" break="no"/>jvanā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tiṁmāryākhyēna gōraṁṭlagaṇakāgrēsarēṇaca <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śilāmayē śāsanēsmin saṁskṛta ślōka vūrvakaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="4"/>lēkhitaṁ dēśabhāṣābhi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> rjīyādācaṁdratārakaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīrēśvaradēvara vidvāṁsa cāṭakū
<lb n="5"/><unclear>ra</unclear>basavaṇasōmayājigaḷu vīrapaṁṇayyanavara sēnabōva tiṁmapanū barasida I (Ī) dēvaru
<lb n="6"/>gaḷa grāmasīmāvṛtti kṣētrādigaḷa śāsanagaḷa prati I(Ī) śilāśā
<lb n="7"/>sanagaḷige maṁgaḷamahā śrī śrī śrī jēyanu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

